{"tid":808633,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意打籃球同埋打麻雀又冇腳既入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-09-06T13:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T17:58:42.000Z","uid":52305,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0471bb4c0032e57b51b586ad72096409598db92e","tid":808633,"uid":52305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"自己想召集一班固定嘅腳一齊打波同埋打麻雀，因為呢兩樣野都係我嘅興趣所以我會選擇呢兩種<br />\n<br />\n由於係希望可以長期夾到所以都想收窄少少範圍<br />\n<br />\n1. 願意喺將軍澳區或者觀塘區活動<br />\n2. 放假係平日夜晚同埋星期六日及公眾假期<br />\n3. 最好30歲樓下，啱傾啲，不限男女<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人同我一樣，返工耐左想約人做以上呢啲活動都係好難約，倒不如自己組一團，固定得閒出嚟做以上活動<br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣嘅就留個TG，希望個群組人數唔會太多，可以固定聚會收夠就算，依家開PO試試水溫"},{"pid":"2c0f18be592b3a52b5b126c98d2ace0b66fbf922","tid":808633,"uid":52305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:43:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joko118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoko118&d=33ZlhKVvrwGLRFUT9hC9CQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=af77d782\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joko118</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣就打個招呼啦"},{"pid":"81c52209fe9b835b40d41a027e9d0686d82df924","tid":808633,"uid":185916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"打麻雀有無地方先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189e546acb7ed1981e6e51261cc33eeead5cd79b","tid":808633,"uid":52305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81c52209fe9b835b40d41a027e9d0686d82df924","tid":808633,"uid":185916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"打麻雀有無地方先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:52:31.000Z","msg":"不定期有，睇大家"},{"pid":"1a07244a7fe15bca69916131f828a3126789d54b","tid":808633,"uid":52305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e579ffa7218a7ac9db71878226dd17871d8df3e","tid":808633,"uid":52305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0